RAY: --do some transposition.

00:33:43.970 --> 00:33:47.590
But at any rate-- oboe, nice.

00:33:47.590 --> 00:33:55.630
So basically, like
I said, we treat--

00:33:55.630 --> 00:33:57.340
we'll play this
